items.title: House unveils stopgap measure to keep government funded, avert shutdown
items.description: The continuing resolution bill will go to the House Rules Committee on Monday and a floor vote is expected Tuesday.

items.title: Chiefs wide receiver Xavier Worthy arrested on domestic assault charge

items.title: 3 men randomly shoot at customers in Toronto pub, wounding 12

items.title: 2 dogs rescued after being kidnapped, ransomed for over $1 million
items.description: The dogs' kidnappers tried to ransom the animals for over $1,135,000, Swiss police said Saturday.
